<!-- This div contains the letter itselfs. Additions to the text are contained in <add/> elements, struck text in <hi> elements with the attribute 'strikethrough' set to true. -->
<div type="content">
<ab><expan>L<ex>ieber</ex></expan> Diecz, als ir uns
                            <expan>verschr<ex>iben</ex></expan> habt von
                            <expan>uns<ex>er</ex>s</expan>
<expan>b<ex>urgers</ex></expan>
<expan>weg<ex>en</ex></expan>
<expan>Ulr<ex>ich</ex></expan> Ortliebs etc., das
                            <expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan> wir wol <expan>vernom<ex>en</ex></expan>
                        und lassen ewch <expan>wiss<ex>en,</ex></expan> daz
                            <expan>ders<ex>elb</ex></expan>
<expan>uns<ex>er</ex></expan>
<expan>b<ex>urger</ex></expan> zu <expan>dis<ex>en</ex></expan>
<expan>zeit<ex>en</ex></expan> niht anheim ist. Wie
                            <expan>daru<ex>m</ex>b</expan> dewcht ewch, daz ir zu
                                <expan>dems<ex>elben</ex></expan> Ortlieb icht <expan>zu
                                sprech<ex>en</ex></expan> hett, <expan>daru<ex>m</ex>b</expan>
<expan>well<ex>e</ex>n</expan> wir ewch <expan>od<ex>er</ex></expan>
<expan>ew<ex>r</ex>m</expan>
<expan>scheinbott<ex>en</ex></expan> mit <expan>ew<ex>r</ex>m</expan>
<expan>voll<ex>e</ex>n</expan> gwalt <expan>frewntl<ex>ich</ex></expan>
                        slewnigs <expan>recht<ex>en</ex></expan> gern
                            <expan>helff<ex>en</ex></expan> vor des reichs
                            <expan>richt<ex>er</ex></expan> bey uns zu
                            <expan>Nür<ex>emberg,</ex></expan> wenn wir des ermant
                                <expan>w<ex>er</ex>den,</expan> so <expan>ders<ex>elb</ex></expan>
<expan>uns<ex>er</ex></expan>
<expan>b<ex>urger</ex></expan> anheim ist, on
                            <expan>gev<ex>er</ex>de</expan>. Und getrawn ewch auch wol, ir lat ewch
                        des <expan>benüg<ex>en</ex></expan>. <expan>Dat<ex>um.</ex></expan>
</ab>
